title: NIBBI Throttle Twist Grips Cable Handlebar Grip Kit Mini Dirt Pit Bike ATV Quad
item_description:
NIBBI RACING Motorcycle Throttle Assembly Universal For CRF50 KLX SSR TTR 110 125 150 200 250cc Dirt Pit Bike ATV Mini Bike,etc
 Premium Aluminum Alloy Throttle Handle
Crafted from top-grade aluminum alloy, this throttle handle is built for exceptional strength, durability, and long-lasting performance.
Comfort Grip Hand Grips
Featuring pillow-top hand grips that eliminate vibration and cushion impact, these grips provide a comfortable, non-slip hold, reducing hand fatigue during long rides.
Smooth and Flexible Throttle Cable
The throttle cable is made with a 316 stainless steel wire core and a trivalent chromium process, ensuring smooth and flexible operation.
Universal Fit NIBBI 43" Throttle Cable
Designed to fit most motorcycles, the NIBBI 43" throttle cable and hand grips have the following dimensions:
Hand Grips Inner Diameter (Left/Right): 22mm/24mm
Twist Throttle Length: 155mm
Inner Diameter: 22mm
Outer Diameter: 26mm
 Features:
Easy to install, durable in use.
Multi-color collocation, wider selection.
Complete modification kit, convenient and quickly.
 Specification:

Throttle Cable Total Length: 110cm
Throttle Cable Moving Length: 15cm
Throttle Twist Grip Length: 155mm
Throttle Twist Grip Inner diameter: 22mm
Throttle Twist Grip Outer diameter: 26mm
Handlebar Grip Left Inner diameter: 22mm
Handlebar Grip Right Inner diameter: 24mm
Handlebar Material:Aluminum Alloy / Plastic
Twist Grip Material: Rubber
Throttle Cable Material: PVC protective sleeve, Metal chrome wire core
 Package include:

1x Throttle Cable
2x Throttle Twist Grips
1x Handlebar Grip
           About NIBBI
Payment
Delivery details
Return Policy
Contact us
- NIBBI RACING was founded in 1983 by Marino Nibbi and Pete Nibbi.
- The company transitioned from general power machinery to specialized racing parts.
- NIBBI RACING focuses on the design and innovation of motocross racing carburetors.
- The company offers a comprehensive system for motorcycles, including various components like fuel supply, air intake, control, drive, electrical control, brake,          suspension, and engine components.
- NIBBI RACING gathers performance feedback from events like MXGP, Romaniacs, Erzberg, and Dakar to enhance and innovate its offerings.
- The company manages global operations through three key centers: Brand Operations Center in California, Technical Research and Development Center in Frankfurt, and Procurement and Supply Center in Canton, China.
- NIBBI RACING team members are passionate professionals dedicated to enhancing off-road motorcycling by providing performance modifications and customized solutions for motorcycle enthusiasts worldwide.
